habitat: With Taraxacum officinale, Carex, Salix lasiolepis, Rosa, Cercocarpus ledifolius, Quercus chrysolepis, Pinus jeffreyi, Eriophyllum confertiflorum, Spenosciadium capitellatum, Stachys albens, Amelanchier utahensis. On NW-facing rock face just above drainage.
locality: San Bernardino Mountains: Tributary of Coon Creek, off FS road 1N02 Elev. given as 7503ft.
